{"tid":952562,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[劣食] IU被台灣食物收買 自豪這部位最美「阿媽也說讚」","createTime":"2018-12-23T09:02:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-23T10:46:29.000Z","uid":34643,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"551025d5f7b83cb8a1e3016b0a19e272bfd0b788","tid":952562,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T09:02:10.000Z","msg":"韓國人氣歌手IU將於平安夜、聖誕節在南港展覽館開唱，兩場門票已經賣完，今（23）日她與媒體見面，聊到聖誕節最印象深刻的回憶，就是7歲時，爸媽都會在聖誕樹下準備很多禮物，早上最期待的就是拆禮物，她也表示，每份禮物都是對方的心意，至今沒有收過讓她不滿意的，而且笑說，如果送她車輪餅的話也OK。<br />\n<br />\n其實IU 22日下午就抵台，逛了兩趟光華商場、士林夜市，自己也在IG透露買了知名的紅豆餅，開心分享：「有找到類似展覽的地方、適合散步的路跟小商店，也跟工作人員買了很多紀念品！」聊到吃的，IU笑說知道紅豆餅店非常有名，所以紅豆、奶油、高麗菜、韭菜口味都有嚐試，大讚「真的很美味」。<br />\n<br />\n她透露在聖誕節訪台的原因，表示可以在台灣度過非常開心，「所以在準備演唱會的時候，就希望演唱會本身能成為大家的禮物，演唱會的內容也有準備禮物送給粉絲的歌。」IU也提到，她國中三年級就出道，所以每年聖誕節都在工作中度過，印象深刻的回憶，是在7歲前，爸媽會在當天準備很多禮物放聖誕樹下，每次都很期待早上拆禮物的時刻。<br />\n<br />\n聊到吃的，IU似乎非常開心，主持人阿達就開玩笑問：「是不是很容易被食物收買？」她就大笑說：「食物很容易收買我，對我來說，願意分享食物的舉動，是一件很溫暖的事情，會覺得對方的心很寬大；而IU也曾多次被入選「世界最美臉孔」，問起最滿意的部位？她笑說是眉毛，因為：「阿媽小時候都說我眉毛跟耳朵最好看！」<br />\n<br />\nIU《2018 IU 10th Anniversary Tour Concert &lt;이지금 dlwlrma&gt; in Taipei》24、25日兩天晚間7點半在南港展覽館開唱，門票已經賣完，她表示，能在台灣度過兩天，很開心也非常興奮，韓國天氣很冷，台灣現在的天氣我很喜歡、很舒服，覺得能在好天氣下跟大家度過，令她開心又期待，希望大家帶著輕鬆心情去到會場享受她的演唱會。<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/nownews.com/dce87a767b86c6598367c7966f2e7d5f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fnownews.com%2Fdce87a767b86c6598367c7966f2e7d5f&h=580b189a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/nownews.com/cbc7062cc2cf2edc25e3334be3ede6d2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fnownews.com%2Fcbc7062cc2cf2edc25e3334be3ede6d2&h=942fe34a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/nownews.com/4c6d2ad4da32e5092ba48ca931661825\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fnownews.com%2F4c6d2ad4da32e5092ba48ca931661825&h=78f397e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/nownews.com/86d02c18a96c3be8c44fbeab9a5803e4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fnownews.com%2F86d02c18a96c3be8c44fbeab9a5803e4&h=c92959b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/nownews.com/7c4c5d01592bc493e5fa31c9ba6d2468\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fnownews.com%2F7c4c5d01592bc493e5fa31c9ba6d2468&h=648f11a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/nownews.com/881ac647367bcfe8e16a2039a44c8a77\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fnownews.com%2F881ac647367bcfe8e16a2039a44c8a77&h=cfdb9228&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/nownews.com/14f34831ce4576bfd12afc616aee1b2e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fnownews.com%2F14f34831ce4576bfd12afc616aee1b2e&h=f81257e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"318efb4b7326485c355c4118224c3ca3be3a2445","tid":952562,"uid":56649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T09:04:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed2f6c7991216d06be6b6c0d09f3dd68b0d99ea9","tid":952562,"uid":77092,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T09:15:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"68287a5d789ce4a6824c4123bf3bfec6867e1858","tid":952562,"uid":46435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T09:18:11.000Z","msg":"IU=天使"},{"pid":"7dca45c09654eec285155678e96c38e297ff19a9","tid":952562,"uid":188733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T09:50:53.000Z","msg":"同IU BB掃街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"h